{"tid":2214831,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"【獨立音樂介紹】通往夢境既浪漫 — 日本Shoegaze","createTime":"2020-09-23T13:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T07:28:40.000Z","uid":159033,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a76040ee4c2fda3cad373a46ebdba6ad16dbac2d","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:55:37.000Z","msg":"<em><strong>通往夢境既浪漫 &mdash; 日本Shoegaze</strong></em><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDDQSGc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDDQSGc.jpg&h=0039e0f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果有一種音樂能夠令人聽落感覺好似墜入左夢境之中咁，會係幾咁浪漫同迷人。</strong><br />\n<br />\n夢幻躁動既Shoegaze（瞪鞋搖滾）正正係呢種迷幻藥，能夠帶我們墜進夢境，呼喚青春既可能性。<br />\n90年代初正值英倫Shoegaze風潮爆發，連遠在東洋既日本人都玩埋一份，經過咁多年來既發展，逐漸形成J-Pop式旋律，日語演唱風格既「和式Shoegaze」，帶俾樂迷耳目一新既聽覺體驗 。<br />\n<br />\n首先當然要介紹左90年代頭既一班傳奇樂隊先啦，包括有<strong>「90年代Shoegaze御三家」: Paint In Watercolour、Loco-Holidays、White Come Come</strong>，帶大家返去果個風起雲湧既搖滾年代！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>「90年代Shoegaze御三家」 Part 1</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>1. 日瞪始組 Paint In Watercolour</em> </strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sr2RBZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSr2RBZ4.jpg&h=70081edd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4U4W73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4U4W73.jpg&h=ea2517e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自新潟縣既Paint In Watercolour可以話係日本最早玩Shoegaze既樂隊，由四個熱愛英倫音樂既架仔組成於80年代尾，佢地深受當時英國Shoegaze、Madchester風潮同埋日本澀谷系音樂既影響，將流行既英倫結他曲調浸入日式風格，而係佢地既身上都可以搵到The Stone Roses、My Bloody Valentine、 Ride等英倫結他樂隊既影子。<br />\n<br />\n1992年既第一張專輯《Unknown》所有歌都係以英語歌詞去演唱，仲帶有日本人獨特既英文唱腔，係當時日本既獨立音樂圏中都算幾另類。《Unknown》既唱片封面超似英國傳奇Shoegaze樂隊My Bloody Valentine既《Isn&rsquo;t Anything》，兩者都係以朦朧,模糊不清的人影作為封面。 到1993年既《Velocity》就變成完全用日文演唱，以流行結他曲調作主導，shoegaze noise 雖然微微減弱，但仍然不失悦耳動人既旋律節奏感。<br />\n<br />\nPaint In Watercolour一共發行左兩張專輯《Unknown》、《Velocity》以及三張EP《In These Things》、《Flow 》、《Glare》就宣告解散，於風起雲湧既90年代，活躍既時間只有短短兩三年，往後再搵不到任何佢地既消息或者近況，同當年既Shoegaze樂潮一樣，難逃曇花一現既命運。但係隨着近呢幾年Shoegaze復興，可以相信既係，Paint In Watercolour絕對己經成為日本Shoegaze既一大傳奇名字了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yEyTeEcqswk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyEyTeEcqswk&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=78c0bba0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yEyTeEcqswk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MbuuGzVC65g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMbuuGzVC65g&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=d66d5694\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MbuuGzVC65g</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家多多支持，有聽開日本Shoegaze既朋友都歡迎一齊傾下計，下期會繼續「90年代Shoegaze御三家」 Part 2！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d240250e64f7c80d83f216e106e24cd9c7741b96","tid":2214831,"uid":117631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:14:51.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"6c1e2c90f83a370104298feae673b7d0ffb0d0bd","tid":2214831,"uid":203614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:21:42.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"cf9c776c7c89caa3fcdbd85b706d6c08f6c0ff21","tid":2214831,"uid":69115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:46:25.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"},{"pid":"bb53cc0058f419957f72890606ed999f0887aafb","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:26:31.000Z","msg":"Paint in Watercolour - Velocity (1993)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-zXEJPyeW08&amp;ab_channel=69gangstar69\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-zXEJPyeW08%26ab_channel%3D69gangstar69&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=12ae5658\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-zXEJPyeW08&amp;ab_channel=69gangstar69</a>"},{"pid":"f4f822163852976bfba0efb9d266b304b895bb53","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"Paint in Watercolour / Velocity (1993)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-zXEJPyeW08&amp;ab_channel=69gangstar69\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-zXEJPyeW08%26ab_channel%3D69gangstar69&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=12ae5658\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-zXEJPyeW08&amp;ab_channel=69gangstar69</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣要提一提，就係佢地1993年既第二張碟《Velocity》其實係幾有傳奇性的，因為呢張碟全部歌都係日文歌詞，佢地亦都係當時日本第一隊Shoegaze樂隊嘗試將日文歌詞搭落去呢種音樂度，同埋可以聽得出佢地都嘗試去建立自己既音樂風格，而唔係一味去Copy人地既野，佢地既態度同做法無疑影響往後好多樂隊去效法。"},{"pid":"d16a74383c8ed063053b2606d537bd0fdded39d7","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>「90年代Shoegaze御三家」 Part 2</em><br />\n<br />\n<em>2. 夢幻躁動</em> Loco-Holidays</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZwXWhA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZwXWhA.jpg&h=df6024ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLoco-Holidays以兩男一女既組合形式係90年代頭結成，係著名的澀谷系廠牌Confusion旗下發行了一張Mini-Album(《Engine Flower》1991年)以及兩張EP(《Drive》1992年，《Screw 》1992年)。<br />\n<br />\n當中以1991年發行的Mini-Album《Engine Flower》最為日本瞪鞋樂迷津津樂道，除了以悦耳的男女和聲為賣點，碟中還翻唱了六十年代傳奇搖滾樂隊The Velvet Underground的名曲&ldquo;Femme Fatale&rdquo;，並加入日系Dream Pop元素，令人耳目一新。<br />\n<br />\n與帶有陽剛英倫風的Paint In Watercolour不同，Loco-Holidays將日式流行曲調，與Shoegaze、Dream Pop元素融合，構成其獨特之聲，給予人温柔内儉的感覺，如果説Paint In Watercolour是日本的Ride，那Loco-Holidays便是日本的Slowdive了。<br />\n<br />\n在樂隊解散後不久，女主音兼貝斯手Hideka(松野秀香)繼續其音樂創作之路，以Ruby Ruby Star之名作個人發展，於93年至95年期間發行了數張Album，在2010年發表了首張個人作品《Hideka》，同時也替不少日本廣播電台創作歌曲。兩兄弟成員(上条盛也，上条欽也)及後也組成了Starwagon和Penpals，作為獨立音樂人活躍至今。2013年，Loco-Holidays曾作一夜限定的復活演出，一飽樂迷多年來的相思之苦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rFOcRIYOUOY&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrFOcRIYOUOY%26feature%3Demb_title&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=4b6135cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rFOcRIYOUOY&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HP2hvuRdUE8&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHP2hvuRdUE8%26feature%3Demb_title&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=6a26b3d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HP2hvuRdUE8&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"cc425d452e61f0df0df34c561aecb385ded46b27","tid":2214831,"uid":241514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:39:58.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0ceb9e45401501931b152c5a7f5668635841074a","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T14:17:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>「90年代Shoegaze御三家」 Part 2</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>3. 英式傳承 White Come Come</em></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPEGPHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPEGPHa.jpg&h=5ee9c865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhite Come Come由三男一女係90年代初於大阪組成，佢地發行既作品比其他同期樂隊少得多，只係喺1992年發行左一張EP《Skin》，同年英國知名Indie廠牌Sugarfrost都同佢地發行左12&Prime;黒膠《Broken Bird EP》。<br />\n<br />\n《Skin》EP有幾首歌係男女合唱，四首歌曲都流暢爽快，令人聽得舒服，一開波主打歌&ldquo;Broken Bird&rdquo;為大家帶來典型既Shoegaze結他音牆，&ldquo;Sink&rdquo;送俾我地一陣溫暖而且甜蜜既少男少女之聲，至於尾曲&ldquo;Rise&rdquo;就令大家諗起Ride果種英倫曲風味。<br />\n<br />\n90年代日本瞪鞋三巨頭各有特色，係當時既日本獨立搖滾圏出類拔群，可惜，佢地係短短幾年間就宣告解散，同英國既Shoegaze風潮一樣咁短命。Shoegaze係一場短暫既音樂風潮，都可能係一種必然既宿命吧!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fl3m5jBEIi8&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dfl3m5jBEIi8%26feature%3Demb_title&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=d9070a64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fl3m5jBEIi8&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"8610a2b44538d8d1b9e5823a6c9c649af9e1a455","tid":2214831,"uid":335664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"More"},{"pid":"b51dbe7dceedbf6c871b7f2dd2562acc06e60d5e","tid":2214831,"uid":160611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:28:18.000Z","msg":"少聽shoegaze不過了解左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有趣"},{"pid":"9e457ea459f6c4066fa4b2475253f0ab349dce85","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>「90年代Shoegazer系列」</em></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/400/1*PUFjd7AVG3logc1B3G1iyg.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F400%2F1%2APUFjd7AVG3logc1B3G1iyg.jpeg&h=b897bf9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>4. <em>夢中瞪孩</em> Mash</strong><br />\n90年代日本正值澀谷系音樂(Shibuya-kei)風潮，澀谷系樂隊大量吸收西洋音樂元素，把英倫吉他搖滾融入日式風格，大受樂迷好評，同時也有不少樂隊嘗試把Shoegaze與澀谷系搭配結合。<br />\n<br />\nSalon Music由吉田仁與竹中仁見二人所建的組合，早在1980年成立，從80年代當時得令的電子新浪潮，到90年代移籍到小山田圭吾的個人廠牌Trattoria，投身澀谷系風潮。<br />\n<br />\n1995年發行的《Mash》絕對是早期日本Shoegaze界受高度評價的作品之一，也是Salon Music唯一的一張Shoegaze專輯，首曲&quot;Who Just Can&rsquo;t Be Happy&rdquo;已能嗅出濃厚的Shoegaze味道，整張專輯充斥Dream Pop式夢幻氛圍及澀谷系動人旋律。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xLjq2aYnxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xLjq2aYnxw&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=9b89dfd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xLjq2aYnxw</a>"},{"pid":"ba717ff0d32dab20732119a03fa5decfa609f75e","tid":2214831,"uid":25759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"16f09acec1d9cef13d75b675e496bcd78b688dd5","tid":2214831,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T23:55:23.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9076352dfb04b106c5ed36c6aeaebe12ddc04cb3","tid":2214831,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T20:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1f1ba0fc8750f4c2cc4abf52ae9273160a3b6e","tid":2214831,"uid":134739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T18:17:36.000Z","msg":"樓主開ig  我一定科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fa0ac0d842433a26ce0e4b899b5b7b30a44a96","tid":2214831,"uid":58352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"樓主係未好多年前係高登開過類似既post，似曾相識咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccf13cc7953b453c67a66b69cbb973504a2b4a3","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>「90年代Shoegazer系列」</em></strong><br />\n<strong><em>5. <em>迷幻瞪社 Incense</em></em></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/424/0*n8dIidcm5SFJaayw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F424%2F0%2An8dIidcm5SFJaayw&h=ec01944a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n組建於1994年既Incense，喺日本獨立廠牌Cardinal Records發行左四張作品，包括兩張Mini-Album同埋兩張EP，其中以1996年既首張專輯《Meteorites》最受樂迷認識。<br />\n<br />\nIncense既成員接近全女班，只有一位男鼓手，雖然以女成員為主導，但佢地玩既風格一啲都唔温柔同清新，曲風帯啲迷幻噪音既元素，喺當時既Shoegaze scene中可以話係比較另類，果陣時都有日本樂迷形容佢地為&rdquo;Stereolab風格既Boredoms&rdquo;。喺網上搵到既Live video入面，佢地玩既歌大多數係&rdquo;Everytime I See You&rdquo;，相信呢首歌都係佢地最具代表性既作品。<br />\n<br />\n題外話，兩位樂隊成員Aki，Maki曾經替日本電子樂隊Color Filter作客席主音，喺97,98年左右Incense解散後，Maki同Michiko Endo組左一隊玩Ambient既樂隊 Ikebana，喺2010年發行專輯《From Dusk Till Dusk》，繼續佢既音樂創作。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tNFU1gJxcZE&amp;t=169s&amp;ab_channel=BlueNoizer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtNFU1gJxcZE%26t%3D169s%26ab_channel%3DBlueNoizer&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=7ab319a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tNFU1gJxcZE&amp;t=169s&amp;ab_channel=BlueNoizer</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eO19R7ftE40&amp;feature=emb_title&amp;ab_channel=incenseaki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeO19R7ftE40%26feature%3Demb_title%26ab_channel%3Dincenseaki&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=fac0f817\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eO19R7ftE40&amp;feature=emb_title&amp;ab_channel=incenseaki</a>"},{"pid":"a1026eabde340d33a1a0e4ab9599a74b4ccc0c3c","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30fa0ac0d842433a26ce0e4b899b5b7b30a44a96","tid":2214831,"uid":58352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"樓主係未好多年前係高登開過類似既post，似曾相識咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"唔記得啦，可能有講過日本Shoegaze野~"},{"pid":"a92418cb46a337c21b48fb87e0f1e68c8aa5ac26","tid":2214831,"uid":134739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1026eabde340d33a1a0e4ab9599a74b4ccc0c3c","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30fa0ac0d842433a26ce0e4b899b5b7b30a44a96","tid":2214831,"uid":58352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"樓主係未好多年前係高登開過類似既post，似曾相識咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"唔記得啦，可能有講過日本Shoegaze野~"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪專攻日本shoegaze?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb1e4bf2c57c0a309e6cef77945f78b4cc3ae5b","tid":2214831,"uid":171942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6baa69fe77604f4601f56dc7fed96f13e58c599","tid":2214831,"uid":156724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:43:39.000Z","msg":"留名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7392272c15c1c357925fa6a456151752b5ec91","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a92418cb46a337c21b48fb87e0f1e68c8aa5ac26","tid":2214831,"uid":134739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1026eabde340d33a1a0e4ab9599a74b4ccc0c3c","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30fa0ac0d842433a26ce0e4b899b5b7b30a44a96","tid":2214831,"uid":58352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"樓主係未好多年前係高登開過類似既post，似曾相識咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"唔記得啦，可能有講過日本Shoegaze野~"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪專攻日本shoegaze?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:38:06.000Z","msg":"係呀，因為本身自己都好鍾意日本文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447ef3343cc7079a0ca6cad2cdaa700ce9c72ad2","tid":2214831,"uid":159033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>「90年代Shoegazer系列」</em></strong><br />\n<strong><em>6. 花草瞪孩 Capsule Giants</em></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/578/0*oW2Ygxhs15Yoak6e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F578%2F0%2AoW2Ygxhs15Yoak6e&h=e02d254e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果你仲認為Shoegaze就一定會係高聲浪既噪音搖滾，咁你就大錯特錯了，喺90年代日本有一班年青人鍾情於花草流行樂，抽取當中既悅耳旋律同時興既Shoegaze結合，奏出動人既流行結他樂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.discogs.com/uy4y3hO64PuQR-z6VX9xQfEFZto=/600x372/smart/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(90)/discogs-images/A-1519693-1312200227.jpeg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.discogs.com%2Fuy4y3hO64PuQR-z6VX9xQfEFZto%3D%2F600x372%2Fsmart%2Ffilters%3Astrip_icc%28%29%3Aformat%28jpeg%29%3Amode_rgb%28%29%3Aquality%2890%29%2Fdiscogs-images%2FA-1519693-1312200227.jpeg.jpg&h=61af4776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCapsule Giants係一支來自福岡縣既三人樂隊，喺1994年11月結成，成員包括主音及結他手横溝礼央，結他手坂井大輔以及鼓手梶原一興。2001年，東京瞪鞋團Evil Daddy Dirt既吉他手田村章加入，擔當樂隊既貝斯手。喺1998年佢地更與美國Noise Pop名團Rocketship共同發行7吋 EP 《Since You Broke My Heart》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.discogs.com/EPrykn5l70UirEXE0dpwA6y5yRs=/fit-in/598x600/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(90)/discogs-images/R-2156524-1267050282.jpeg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.discogs.com%2FEPrykn5l70UirEXE0dpwA6y5yRs%3D%2Ffit-in%2F598x600%2Ffilters%3Astrip_icc%28%29%3Aformat%28jpeg%29%3Amode_rgb%28%29%3Aquality%2890%29%2Fdiscogs-images%2FR-2156524-1267050282.jpeg.jpg&h=339c1129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地同名團Paint In Watercolour一樣深受時興既澀谷系同Madchester風潮影響，成員們都非常熱愛Indie Pop同C86，所以專輯入面並冇太多急速狂躁既結他噪音，反而以一首首動聽既結他流行曲為賣點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.discogs.com/dMSVxgJyd7TQRV_buQXByGCAF9I=/fit-in/600x605/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(90)/discogs-images/R-1861796-1248505535.jpeg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.discogs.com%2FdMSVxgJyd7TQRV_buQXByGCAF9I%3D%2Ffit-in%2F600x605%2Ffilters%3Astrip_icc%28%29%3Aformat%28jpeg%29%3Amode_rgb%28%29%3Aquality%2890%29%2Fdiscogs-images%2FR-1861796-1248505535.jpeg.jpg&h=a2072b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1996年既《Hey Cow-Planet》可以話係Capsule Giants最悅耳動人以及具備Shoegaze味道既專輯，&rdquo;Don&rsquo;t Forget Me&rdquo;正係典型既Shoegaze/Noise Pop歌曲、&rdquo;Ever Blurs&rdquo;充斥住濃厚既Madchester舞曲味道，甚有英國經典樂隊Happy Mondays既影子、&rdquo;Apple Girl-506&Prime;更加入卡祖笛作演奏。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.discogs.com/JI00O7dBxCXR5FmwwMffmLTzlFc=/fit-in/300x300/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(40)/discogs-images/R-3023550-1312199242.jpeg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.discogs.com%2FJI00O7dBxCXR5FmwwMffmLTzlFc%3D%2Ffit-in%2F300x300%2Ffilters%3Astrip_icc%28%29%3Aformat%28jpeg%29%3Amode_rgb%28%29%3Aquality%2840%29%2Fdiscogs-images%2FR-3023550-1312199242.jpeg.jpg&h=8a154283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可惜自2002年發行《WE LOVE NEW DARK》之後就再冇任何活動，官方網站都停止左更新，到左2004年，成員們組建左另一支樂隊NEON GROUP，進行其他音樂類型既嘗試了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cQlYyknNOxs&amp;feature=emb_title&amp;ab_channel=shima999jun\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcQlYyknNOxs%26feature%3Demb_title%26ab_channel%3Dshima999jun&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=a225438e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cQlYyknNOxs&amp;feature=emb_title&amp;ab_channel=shima999jun</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eoQR2OH0-sI&amp;feature=emb_title&amp;ab_channel=RIMBAUDONRITALIN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeoQR2OH0-sI%26feature%3Demb_title%26ab_channel%3DRIMBAUDONRITALIN&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=1c485e6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eoQR2OH0-sI&amp;feature=emb_title&amp;ab_channel=RIMBAUDONRITALIN</a>"},{"pid":"fb51c30759049ba864601c901d53d652e77a6bff","tid":2214831,"uid":6425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"日本shoegaze最鍾意<br />\nTokyo shoegazer <br />\nMonocism<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}